What is Data?
Data is information about everything
Name, surename, birthday, description, numbers and so on

Computer files, Images, excel files

What is a Database?
It is organized collection of data
list of employees with their associated data

Why data must be organized?
It can be easily accessed, managed and updated
To retreive certained data from database in a certain condition

Database functtionally
Store and manipulate the data
For manipulation of the data a special queary language is used
Different ways of organizing the data - relational/ non relational
